# PHASE 3 — Node Lifecycle Hooks

This is where V3 starts feeling premium.

---

## Add Structured Lifecycle

Instead of random execution:

```js id="a1gtt6"
onBeforeEnter()
onEnter()
onAfterRender()
onExit()
```

NOT arbitrary JS hooks.

Runtime-owned lifecycle phases.

---

# Why This Matters

This enables:

* timed reveals
* audio triggers
* cinematic fades
* analytics
* overlays
* auto-saving
* transition effects

…without stuffing logic into renderer.

